                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- The hymn Śarāwita malāʾǝktihu la-Madḫāne ʿĀlam “The hosts of the angels
                        of the Savior of the world” is occasionally written in compressed script (s.
                           <locus target="#85vb">85vb</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
