                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits and headings of the texts;
                           directives for the ministers; the abbreviations; some of the musical
                           notation signs above the lines; elements of the punctuation signs and
                           Ethiopic numerals.
 On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 3r) and of
                           Anaphoras (fols. 35r, 48r, 51r, 59v, 66v, 72v, 77v, 82r, 86v, 91r, 100r,
                           113r), few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</seg>
